    </p>
    <p>
      The physical wheel used in Crazy Time is independently certified. Results cannot be manipulated by the casino because the game is hosted entirely by Evolution — casinos receive a live video feed, they do not control the outcome. This is fundamentally different from software slots where the operator controls the RNG. Read more in our <a href="/crazy-time-is-it-rigged">Is Crazy Time Rigged?</a> breakdown.
    </p>
