    <h2>Real Money Payouts — What to Expect</h2>
    <p>
      Crazy Time payouts depend entirely on which segment the wheel lands on and whether a top slot multiplier applies. Here's a quick reference:
    </p>
    <ul>
      <li><strong>Segment 1</strong>: pays 1:1 — a $1 bet returns $1 profit</li>
      <li><strong>Segment 2</strong>: pays 2:1 — a $1 bet returns $2 profit</li>
